<leg xml:space="preserve" billnum="HJR023" sponsor="Ryan D. Wilcox" designation="HJR" otherSponsor="" otherHouse="Senate" sess="2026GS" fileno="2026FL0598" date="2/9/2026 08:02:810" printDate="02-09 08:27" subVer="0" minVer="0" office="LEGISLATIVE GENERAL COUNSEL" actionDate="" impact="brules"><info><nextbuid>7</nextbuid><aminfo anum="0" effdate="01/01/1800"><seclist><sect action="E" src="rule" buid="6" uid="JR1-4-S604_1800010118000101" sort="J01 04 06040018000101" mtype="section" effdate="01/01/1800">JR1-4-604</sect><sect src="uncod" untype="effdate" buid="5" uid="EF0000" sort="UZEFF" mtype="uncod" effdate="01/01/1800"/></seclist></aminfo></info><tbox><sinfo><nextpairid>0</nextpairid></sinfo><st numlevel="1" lineno="1" slineno="0-1">Joint Rules Resolution - Policy Development and Impact</st><sessionhead>2026 GENERAL SESSION</sessionhead><statehead>STATE OF UTAH</statehead><sponsorhead>Chief Sponsor: Ryan D. Wilcox</sponsorhead><otherSponsorhead>Senate Sponsor: </otherSponsorhead></tbox><lt numlevel="1" lineno="2" slineno="0-2"><lthead lineno="3">LONG TITLE</lthead><gdhead lineno="4">General Description:</gdhead><gd numlevel="1" lineno="5" slineno="0-5">This joint rules resolution enacts provisions related to policy development and impact.</gd><hphead lineno="6">Highlighted Provisions:</hphead><hp numlevel="1" lineno="7" slineno="0-7">This resolution:<hl numlevel="1" lineno="8" slineno="0-8" level="1">requires the chief sponsor of legislation to specify the policy problem and measurable <ln numlevel="1" lineno="9" slineno="0-9"/>objectives to evaluate the impact of the legislation;</hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="10" slineno="0-10" level="1">requires the Office of Legislative Research and General Counsel to assist with developing <ln numlevel="1" lineno="11" slineno="0-11"/>policy and ensure that legislation's drafting instructions include certain information; and</hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="12" slineno="0-12" level="1">authorizes the Office of the Legislative Auditor General, when conducting an audit, to <ln numlevel="1" lineno="13" slineno="0-13"/>request certain information from the Office of Legislative Research and General <ln numlevel="1" lineno="14" slineno="0-14"/>Counsel.</hl></hp><moni numlevel="1" lineno="15" slineno="0-15" display="none">Money Appropriated in this Bill:</moni><moniNone lineno="16">None</moniNone><oc numlevel="1" lineno="17" slineno="0-17">Other Special Clauses:<ocl type="effdate" sort="2" numlevel="1" lineno="18" slineno="0-18">None</ocl></oc><ra numlevel="1" lineno="19" slineno="0-19">Legislative Rules Affected:<raent numlevel="1" lineno="20" slineno="0-20"><snhead>ENACTS:</snhead><sn num="JR1-4-604" src="rule" uid="JR1-4-S604_1800010118000101" buid="6" sort="J01 04 06040018000101" numlevel="1" lineno="21" slineno="0-21"><bold>JR1-4-604</bold></sn></raent></ra></lt><enacthead lineno="22"/><enact numlevel="1" lineno="23" slineno="0-23">Be it resolved by the Legislature of the state of Utah:</enact><bdy><bsec buid="6" num="JR1-4-604" type="enact" src="rule" uid="JR1-4-S604_1800010118000101" sort="J01 04 06040018000101" numlevel="1" lineno="24" slineno="1-1" sn="1"><section numlevel="1" lineno="26" slineno="1-3" number="JR1-4-604" type="enact"><secline lineno="24">Section 1. <bold>JR1-4-604</bold> is enacted to read:</secline><headpart number="JR1-4-6" numlevel="1" lineno="25" slineno="1-2">6. <amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="29" groupid="23" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="both">Performance, Efficiency, and Policy Impact Reporting</amend></headpart><catline lineno="26"><bold>JR1-4-604<parens/>. Policy development and impact.</bold></catline><subsection ssid="6-1" dnum="_-o:1-i" numlevel="1" lineno="27" slineno="1-4" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1" placement="noreturn"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1000" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(1)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="13" groupid="10" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">After filing a request for legislation under <xref depth="3" refnumber="JR4-2-101">JR4-2-101</xref>, the chief sponsor shall, in <ln numlevel="1" lineno="28" slineno="1-5"/>consultation with the Office of Legislative Research and General Counsel:</amend><subsection ssid="6-2" dnum="_-o:a-i" numlevel="1" lineno="29" slineno="1-6" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1001" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(a)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="12" groupid="9" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">specify the policy problem the chief sponsor aims to address with the legislation; and</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="6-3" dnum="_-o:b-i" numlevel="1" lineno="30" slineno="1-7" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1002" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(b)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="18" groupid="14" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">identify the chief sponsor's policy goal and one or more measurable objectives to <ln numlevel="1" lineno="31" slineno="1-8"/>evaluate whether the legislation effectively addresses the policy problem.</amend></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="6-4" dnum="_-o:2-i" numlevel="1" lineno="32" slineno="1-9" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1003" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(2)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="23" groupid="18" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">The Office of Legislative Research and General Counsel shall:</amend><subsection ssid="6-7" dnum="_-o:a-i" numlevel="1" lineno="33" slineno="1-10" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1004" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(a)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="39" groupid="31" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">assist with developing the chief sponsor's policy in preparation for drafting the <ln numlevel="1" lineno="34" slineno="1-11"/>sponsor's legislation; and</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="6-8" dnum="_-o:b-i" numlevel="1" lineno="35" slineno="1-12" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1005" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(b)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="44" groupid="35" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">ensure that the drafting instructions for a request for legislation include the policy <ln numlevel="1" lineno="36" slineno="1-13"/>information described in Subsection <xref depth="4" refnumber="JR1-4-604(1)">(1)</xref>.</amend></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="6-5" dnum="_-o:3-i" numlevel="1" lineno="37" slineno="1-14" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1006" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(3)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="28" groupid="22" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">When conducting an audit under Utah Code Section <xref depth="3" refnumber="36-12-15">36-12-15</xref> or <xref depth="3" refnumber="JR1-4-603">JR1-4-603</xref>, the Office <ln numlevel="1" lineno="38" slineno="1-15"/>of the Legislative Auditor General may request from the Office of Legislative Research <ln numlevel="1" lineno="39" slineno="1-16"/>and General Counsel the policy information described in Subsection <xref depth="4" refnumber="JR1-4-604(1)">(1)</xref> for the purpose <ln numlevel="1" lineno="40" slineno="1-17"/>of evaluating the impact of Utah statutes that are relevant to the audit.</amend></subsection></section></bsec><bsec buid="5" type="uncod" untype="effdate" src="uncod" uid="EF0000" sort="UZEFF" langlock="false" numlevel="1" lineno="41" slineno="2-1" sn="2"><section type="uncod" untype="effdate" display="false" src="uncod"><secline lineno="41">Section 2.  <bold>Effective Date.</bold></secline><sectionText lineno="42"><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1" groupid="1" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="both">This resolution takes effect upon a successful vote for final passage.</amend></sectionText></section></bsec></bdy><foot><rev><tm>2-9-26 8:27 AM</tm></rev></foot></leg>